1
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:41,159
Look at these holes on the pillars.

2
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:43,320
That's pretty strange.

3
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,400
Watch it, fatty! You almost hit me!

4
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,280
You punk.

5
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,920
Be careful. It might be a trap.

6
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,680
Nothing's happening.

7
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,760
Nothing above, nothing below.

8
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,799
Nothing in the distance either.

9
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:33,560
I think it's just a ventilation hole.

10
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:35,400
Better safe than sorry.

11
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:35,879
Let's go.

12
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,519
Move.

13
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,439
Wait.

14
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,359
Wha-what's that sound?

15
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,280
Did you hear something?

16
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,319
Stop freaking out.

17
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,760
Maybe I just heard wrong.

18
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,400
Everyone, stick close.

19
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,719
Move.

20
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:15,159
Lao Lu, stop being so jumpy.

21
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,360
You're freaking us out, you know.

22
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,719
An Xiang! An Xiang!

23
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,199
An Xiang! An Xiang!

24
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,199
It's a trap! Take cover!

25
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,759
Hurry, move!

26
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,199
Watch out!

27
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:12,919
Don't move!

28
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,639
Lao Lu!

29
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:19,520
Stay down, don't move.

30
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:22,599
An Xiang, are you okay?

31
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,560
Take off your jacket.

32
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,560
Let me check her wound.

33
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,159
No need.

34
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:26,919
It's fine.

35
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,000
I can manage.

36
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,360
Arrows fire, doors close.

37
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:34,199
Classic linked-trap mechanism.

38
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,280
The only difference is,

39
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,479
before, when we triggered traps,

40
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,919
we'd notice immediately.

41
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,919
But here, aside from these holes,

42
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:41,240
there's nothing.

43
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,800
Lao Lu, crawl over here.

44
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,199
Just stay down, don't move. Good.

45
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,199
Luckily, you're not badly hurt.

46
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:55,919
It didn't hit any bones.

47
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,800
Godfather.

48
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,599
Go ahead.

49
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,520
Actually, lately,

50
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,360
I've been thinking a lot.

51
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,680
If we really find the Lingxiao Pearl,

52
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,960
Bear with it, bear with it.

53
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,759
It needs disinfecting.

54
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,879
If we really find the Lingxiao Pearl,

55
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,079
instead of keeping it ourselves,

56
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,839
why not give it to Brother Chen?

57
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,160
Let them study it.

58
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:26,519
If the Pearl really holds secrets,

59
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:28,879
they'll be way more efficient than us.

60
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,959
The Lingxiao Pearl...

61
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,600
No matter what,

62
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:42,560
the Pearl cannot fall into their hands.

63
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:47,600
I'm counting on it to save your life.

64
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,560
Don't be so naive anymore.

65
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,439
I understand.

66
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,160
The trigger mechanism

67
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,800
might also be inside the wall.

68
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,519
Who are you kidding?

69
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,199
Someone's hiding inside the wall?

70
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,399
Shooting arrows from inside?

71
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,199
It's snakes.

72
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,680
Snakes!

73
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,040
Yes, it's snakes!

74
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,879
Snakes!

75
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,360
Snakes!

76
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,879
I said I heard sounds earlier,

77
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:17,399
that rustling sound,

78
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,120
but nobody believed me.

79
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,000
I'm losing all credibility in this team.

80
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,160
Didn't Advisor He say it?

81
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,639
This is the People of the Serpent God.

82
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,480
Since we came in,

83
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,920
we haven't seen a single snake.

84
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,040
So there's one possibility:

85
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,600
the snakes are inside the walls.

86
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,079
That sound we heard earlier

87
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:38,759
was snakes rubbing against the walls.

88
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,279
Hence the name People of the Serpent God.

89
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:45,519
Hey, everyone,

90
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,800
can we stop chatting?

91
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,639
Find a way to stop the arrows!

92
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:02,920
Only the pillar holes shot arrows.

93
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,879
The door behind you,

94
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,519
and the holes on this door,

95
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,759
didn't shoot any arrows.

96
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,639
Come on, give me a hand.

97
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,879
Aren't you going to help?

98
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:30,000
If an arrow shoots from this side

99
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,040
and passes through that hole,

100
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,759
it might open the door over there.

101
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,639
It's possible.

102
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,560
It's like a linked key.

103
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:38,560
But the snakes are moving on both sides.

104
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,519
How do we lure them to the middle?

105
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,680
Lure the snakes over there?

106
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,199
You think this is a monkey show?

107
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,639
You can't just lure them anywhere you want.

108
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,480
These are snakes.

109
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,279
Shut up, you ignorant fool.

110
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,639
You know what snakes love most?

111
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,720
Mice. Snakes eat mice.

112
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,639
Get out of here.

113
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,959
The smell of blood.

114
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,680
Boss, hurry!

115
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,120
Slow down, slow down.

116
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,720
Looks like snakes are coming!

117
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,319
The door's open!

118
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,920
Lao Lu, hurry over here!

119
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,680
Hurry!

120
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,879
Before the snakes return to the middle,

121
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:45,519
get over here, quick!

122
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,720
Lao Lu, hurry!

123
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,040
Okay.

124
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,959
Let's go!

125
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:51,879
Brother Chen.

126
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:54,000
An Xiang can't go on. She needs a rest.

127
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,839
Okay, everyone take a break here.

128
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:57,839
Shutong, let's go check ahead.

129
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,120
Are you feeling any better?

130
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,839
Chen Youxi!

131
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,240
Chen Youxi!

132
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:39,159
Life and death of all things.

133
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,759
Blessings of the Serpent God.

134
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:48,159
All living beings suffer.

135
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,440
The four directions form a prison.

136
00:11:54,039 --> 00:11:56,679
When three lamps shine together,

137
00:11:57,879 --> 00:12:01,480
all suffering shall end.

138
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:13,639
Chen Youxi!

139
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,600
Can you hear me?

140
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,440
Old Chen!

141
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,320
At least say something!

142
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,240
I'm fine.

143
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,120
Why didn't you say so sooner?

144
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,639
Honestly!

145
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:28,360
Advisor He was worried sick.

146
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:50,960
Are you okay?

147
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,559
I'm fine.

148
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,320
These traps are truly everywhere.

149
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:57,159
I saw some murals down there earlier.

150
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,039
I'm guessing they depict

151
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,799
the Mengnagu people's ceremonial rites.

152
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,519
The Lingxiao Pearl was on the murals too.
